22 is perfect!
Review by Anjana on 30 Apr 2019 review stating 22 is perfect!
Both Kylie matte and velvet formulas are high quality, and last all day/night through eating & drinking. 22 was my first love! It’s the perfect burnt deep orange. I have since fallen in love with the lipstick shades heat, dazzle, ginger and pumpkin- I have tan skin and I tend to like shades with orange/peachy tint which is exactly what these shades are like. If you have tan olive skin like me, heat shows more like a deep red on my lips, dazzle is bright plummy purple, ginger looks like a pretty nude brown and pumpkin is pinkish orangish on my skin tone. Very pretty colors. I highly recommend these top quality lipstick formulas. I haven’t seen anything better anywhere else.
